title: Sri Bannari Amman
subTitle: Goddess Bannari Amman takes the form of a skilled healer, travelling through small villages to cure people's ailments. On her divine mission, she vanquishes evil and blesses the righteous.

title: En Uyir Thozhan
subTitle: Chittu finds herself abandoned and alone until Dharma steps in to help, but his deep loyalty to politics begins to strain the fragile peace they build.

title: Kavari Maan
subTitle: In a moment of rage, a man destroys his family after uncovering his wife's betrayal. Later, he tries to reconnect with his daughter who refuses to forgive him.

title: Kodi Parakuthu
subTitle: A mafia leader tries to kill policeman Sivagiri, who took down his illegal businesses, with the help of a lookalike. Later, Sivagiri discovers that the leader is responsible for his father's death.

title: Mani Kuyil

title: Engal Thanga Raja
subTitle: Manjula falls in love with Raja but he is scared to reciprocate his feelings. Later, he discovers that Manjula's father is the same man who destroyed his sister's life.
